Class AppointmentOutcome

java.lang.Object
AppointmentOutcome.Model.AppointmentOutcome
All Implemented Interfaces:
IEntity
public class AppointmentOutcome extends Object implements IEntity
Represents the outcome of an appointment, including details such as services provided, medication prescribed, and consultation notes.
